{"tid":2121210,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"公務員特別上班安排延長至下月二日","createTime":"2020-07-23T07:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T07:36:05.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"04cfea9487b1a76a8e7f4b0e14c843e9d8e22cfd","tid":2121210,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:25:52.000Z","msg":"政府宣布將公務員特別上班安排，延長一星期到八月二日。 <br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示疫情仍然非常嚴竣，需要繼續大幅減少社區人流和社交接觸，只能提供緊急和必須公共服務，其他僱員需留在家中工作，個別部門會就各項服務的最新安排，另行作出公布。 <br />\n<br />\n有需要的市民可盡量利用郵寄、投遞箱或網上服務等方法，以獲得所需服務。發言人又呼籲私營機構僱主按運作需要，盡量讓員工在家工作，以減少社區人流和社交接觸。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348599&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=33d3a113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348599</a>"},{"pid":"589dea643ec94034fbd3a966c0c5d8cf8f68bb31","tid":2121210,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"19609cee13f8f21516315e07434b961a69d6f3ef","tid":2121210,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"好心就唔好煩<br />\n禁足咪得"},{"pid":"61d1d5f33ba88ee5852817d3b2fd636230df494d","tid":2121210,"uid":362827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"開gym未"},{"pid":"b036d99c0a1221380f14940fe6d151a9a37c6cea","tid":2121210,"uid":358058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"係ab team，唔係在家工作，唔該佢澄清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c04411441be71be8be522e7551d4922e8d5ba1","tid":2121210,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:27:45.000Z","msg":"我要打波啊！"},{"pid":"ea44a57579b94500ec361fbc99a0a94c21c1f265","tid":2121210,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-2